snippet.textDisplay: The Most Realistic and Relatable shot was when Kavish is singing their verses, and Hannan was sitting on stairs and looking down with despair and confusion. This was most authentic and most brilliant depiction of condition he is facing. When you have tried all of your positivity of heart to make sense of this life, people and society around you, but in return you got nothing but negativity and darkness. And, finally you gave up in hopelessness and being alone. Tiredness on his face.... that is so beautiful shot and relatable. Love you Coke Studio
